              "answer": "Dynamic pricing automatically adjusts your nightly rate based on real‑time supply and demand. During quiet periods it nudges prices lower to attract guests; in peak season it lifts rates to capture extra profit, maximising revenue and occupancy.",
              "question": "What Is Dynamic Pricing And Why Does It Matter?"
            },
            {
              "answer": "Most hosts see an average uplift of around 20 %, but properties in high‑traffic areas or with wide seasonal swings often earn even more.",
              "question": "How Much Extra Money Can I Make?"
            },
            {
              "answer": "You remain in charge. MyAllocator gives you suggested rates backed by billions of data points, yet you can override any price or pause automation at any time.",
              "question": "Is There Any Risk?"
            },
            {
              "answer": "Dynamic Pricing is an optional add‑on for all MyAllocator subscribers. Activate it from your dashboard, set your guardrails, and enjoy a risk‑free 30‑day trial.",
              "question": "How Do I Start?"
            },
            {
              "answer": "Every paying MyAllocator customer, whether you manage one cottage or fifty apartments, is eligible for one complimentary 30‑day test drive.",
